snippet.title: Swordigo Gameplay Trailer (Google Play, Android)
snippet.description:
Run, jump and slash your way through a vast world of challenges and embark on an epic adventure!

Get it for free on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.touchfoo.swordigo

Also available on the iOS App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/swordigo/id499125840?mt=8

More details at http://touchfoo.com/swordigo
